data.description: Welcome to your new home, a stunning and spacious family retreat nestled in the heart of picturesque Willard. This enchanting home sits on a large lot on a quiet street making it an ideal place to create lasting memories. Step inside and be greeted by tons of natural light and an open concept. The living area is designed for both family gatherings and entertaining, with an open layout that seamlessly connects the living room, dining room, and kitchen. This home offers a total of three generously sized bedrooms, each with its own unique character and charm. The master suite is a true sanctuary with an en-suite bathroom and a large closet. The backyard is a true oasis and offers plenty of room to roam and unwind. Situated in the charming town of Willard, you're just a short drive away from the town center, schools, and parks. Enjoy the convenience of local amenities while relishing the peaceful ambiance of your own retreat. Don't miss your chance to call this house your next home!
